  core.Graph<E>
Type Parameters:
E - 
public class Graph<E>
extends java.lang.Object

Represents the Graph object. Uses Adjacency List. Internally a Graph is represented by a HashMap Key=Vertex (say V) Value= Linked List of all Vertex where there is an edge between V and this Vertex A Vertex is a wrapper around Graph of the objects being built (E) Supports both directed and undirected graphs
